Package: autograph
Title: Automatic Plotting of Many Graphs
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-11-26
Description: Visual exploration and presentation of networks should not be difficult.
   This package includes functions for plotting networks and network-related metrics
   with sensible and pretty defaults.
   It includes ggplot2-based plot methods for many popular network package classes,
   and three functions for drawing single, comparative, and dynamic graphs.
   It also includes some novel layout algorithms,
   and options for straightforward, consistent theming.
URL: https://stocnet.github.io/autograph/
BugReports: https://github.com/stocnet/autograph/issues
